</li>
<li>
<p>进入项目目录并查看项目结构</p>
<p><img src="http://yinshuaiguo.gitee.io/photo_bed/md_photo/myblog/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hugo%20+%20Gitee%20Pages%20%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/b3.png" alt="1585990502839"></p>
